Sailthru::Client

DOCUMENTATION

http://getstarted.sailthru.com/developers/api-libraries/perl

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Digest::MD5
JSON::XS
LWP::Protocol::https
LWP::UserAgent
Params::Validate
Readonly
URI
Test::MockModule
Test::Exception

